 Angular js
 
 jbox - notices, info box.
 eg-
 new jBox('Notice', {
					attach: $('p_tooltip'),
					content: 'Dealer login requied !!',
					animation: {open: 'tada', close: 'flip'},
					delayClose: 50,
					position: {
							x: 'right',
							y: 'bottom'
							},
					offset: {
							x: -15,
							y: -15
							}
							});
	*************************
	
